name: Woodkeeper
description:
A little raccoon that likes their forest clean. Except for food leftovers.

In the heart of the forest, there's a little raccoon struggling every day to find something to eat amidst all the trash left by humans. They call them the Woodkeeper.

While searching for profitable items in the rubbish, the Woodkeeper chose to also clean their forest. Now their daily mission is to collect as much trash as possible while trying to survive.
